    Attendee

    For reading from a .ser file containing the saved ChatroomManager.
    ChatPush
    For saving ChatroomManager to .ser file.

    Chatroom that stores message history and has methods for sending messages.
    ChatroomManager
    Stores all Chatrooms in the program, deals with adding new Chatrooms and sending messages.

    An abstract presenter that contains the base features for all messaging-related presenters.
    ConferenceSimulator
    This class represents the executable for the application.
    CredentialsUseCase
    Use case which enforces user credentials rules in the registrar.
    Event
    A class representing the event entity.

    A controller for the event class.
    EventCreatorPresenter
    A presenter for the event class.
    EventManager
    Use Case Class that stores all events in the program and enables creation and deletion of events.
    EventSignup
    Use Case class that enables signing up and leaving events.

    Controller that manages signing up and leaving events
    EventSignupPresenter
    Presenter for the event signup process.
    FriendsController
    Controller that manages a user's friends list.
    FriendsManager
    Use case class that stores and removes the names of users to another user's friends list.

    Contains the text display for interacting with the user for managing a users friend's list.
    InboxController
    For taking in user inputs for viewing chat history and replying to messages.
    InboxPresenter
    Contains the text display for viewing chat history and replying to messages.
    Login
    Controller which logs users into the registrar.
    LoginOptionsFacade
    Facade controller which gives various options relating to managing stored users.

    Presenter which gives users information related to login and account management

    A user interface which exchanges inputs and outputs with a person to login/manage their account.
    Main
    Main static method of program.
    Message
    An object that represents a message sent between users
    Organizer
    A class representing an organizer user.
    OrganizerCreationScript
    A class that should rarely change, with a single method that creates as many Organizer instances as needed for a conference.
    OutboxController
    OutboxController handles user requests for sending messages.
    OutboxPresenter
    Handles text format and display for the client.
    ReadEvents
    ReadEvents is a gateway class that reads from a .ser file.
    ReadUsers
    ReadUsers is a gateway class that reads from a .ser file.
    Registrar
    Registrar is the use case class for all interactions with User objects.
    SaveEvents
    SaveEvents is a gateway class that is used to save a list of the available talks at the conference to a .ser file for use in other login sessions.
    Speaker
    This class represents speakers for the events.
    StoreUsers
    StoreUsers is a gateway class that is used to save a list of the users attending the conference to a .ser file for use in other login sessions.
    User
    This is an abstract class that will be used to represent all users.
    UserOptionsInterface
    UserOptionsInterface is the main controller class that handles the home menu controls for a single user's session.
